title: Maybelline New York The Falsies Volum' Express Washable Mascara, Blackest Black, 0.25 Fluid Ounce
description: It's not mascara, it's false lash glam in a tube, instantly  patented spoon brush and pro keratin fiber formula instantly build 8x more volume without clumping. Unique flexible wand helps lift and separate, to provide the look of 3x more lashes. You will find lashes you didn't even know you had. To safeguard maybelline(r) purity, reserve this product for your personal use. Treat the applicator with the hygienic care you give your eyes. never apply this product in a moving vehicle. Do not dilute mascara with water, saliva, or any other substance. Cap tightly after use. if change in odor or appearance occurs, discontinue use. do not use this or any other eye cosmetic if your eye is injured, irritate, or infected. consult a physician promptly.

title: L'Oreal Paris Youth Code Texture Perfector Pore Vanisher, 1.4 Fluid Ounce
description: Instantly diminish the look of pores with L'Oreal Paris Youth Code Texture Perfector Pore Vanisher, a new generation of skincare that effectively works to target multiple dimensions of the pore until pores appear virtually vanished. Instantly micro-exfoliates to smooth skin's surface and absorb excess oil for 8 shine-free hours. Instantly gives a soft-focus finish around the surface of the pore. Over time strengthens and tightens to shrink the appearance of pores, and in 1 month shrinks actual pore size.

title: L'Oreal Paris Ideal Skin Genesis Pore Minimize Gel Cleanser, 8-Fluid Ounce
description: Now, your daily cleanser helps you create smoother, brighter, fresher skin! Introducing Skin Genesis Pore Minimizing Gel Cleanser. With a skin compatible Ph level, this gel cleanser is so gentle that it can be massaged around the eye area, and so efficient that it removes impurities and even eye makeup.
